how I got here.

45
00:07:05,773 --> 00:07:07,296
Come with me.

46
00:07:07,383 --> 00:07:09,254
Uma! Mademoiselle!

47
00:07:09,341 --> 00:07:11,039
Just come with me.

48
00:07:17,480 --> 00:07:18,699
