52
00:07:34,715 --> 00:07:38,109
What is this place?

53
00:08:31,554 --> 00:08:34,426
Excuse me, but, who are you?

54
00:08:34,514 --> 00:08:39,214
Some people complain that
rose bushes have thorns.

55
00:08:39,301 --> 00:08:41,216
I rejoice that...

56
